snippet.title: HoloFist Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the magical world of HoloFist!

WISHLIST ON STEAM TODAY! https://store.steampowered.com/app/774471/HoloFist/

Grab your HoloBuddies and thrown down in turn-based arena battles we like to refer to as "Fist-offs". Join our main girl Mindy as she kicks, fists and existentially drifts her way through the adventure of a lifetime to save the island of 'Fistopia' from the ravages of sceience itself.

Follow HoloFist to catch our updates! https://twitter.com/holofist
